# cache/
#
# In-memory and Redis cache utilities (Phase 4).
#
# Planned modules:
#   memoryCache.js  — lightweight LRU in-process cache (no Redis dep)
#   redisCache.js   — distributed cache backed by Redis
#   cacheKeys.js    — all cache key templates in one place
#   cacheTTL.js     — TTL constants by resource type
#
# Cache strategy per resource:
#   Bus positions   → 15 s TTL (data changes rapidly)
#   Route metadata  → 5 min TTL (changes rarely)
#   Stop data       → 1 h TTL  (almost static)
